News.Title: Delta Autocorp: Strong Market Debut with 30% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Delta Autocorp shares listed at ₹175 on NSE SME, 34.6% above the IPO price of ₹130. The stock closed at ₹169, maintaining a 30% premium. The IPO was oversubscribed 342.1 times. The company, founded in 2016, manufactures electric two and three-wheelers under the brand 'Deltic'.
